Package <Unnamed>

Class Summary
Main The Main class.
Snake A Snake object which is used to describe a snake under the following attributes
SnakeNode SnakeNode is a Node object used by SnakeTree Each node contains a Snake object which can be resolved through SnakeNode.getSnake()
SnakeSimulator The SnakeSimulator is used to determine the maximum MPRS-length song for a given set of snakes.
SnakeTree SnakeTree is a Tree made up of SnakeNode nodes Each node contains a Snake object.
